            </div>
            <div class="ex6">(3) in paragraph (2)(A), by striking ``Board'' and inserting ``Comptroller''; and</div>
            <div class="ex6">
               (4) in paragraph (3)--
               <div class="ex7">(A) by redesignating subparagraphs (A) through (C) as subparagraphs (B) through (D), respectively; and</div>
               <div class="ex7" Notes_1="Definition.">
                  (B) by inserting before subparagraph (B) the following: 
                  <div class="ex7">``(A) Comptroller.--The term `Comptroller' means the Comptroller of the Currency.''.</div>
               </div>
            </div>
