         <div class="ex4">
            SEC. 364. FEDERAL HOME LOAN BANK ACT.
            <div class="ex5" Notes_1="12 USC 1438 note. Effective date.">(a) Repeal of Section 18(c).--Effective 90 days after the transfer date, section 18(c) of the Federal Home Loan Bank Act (12 U.S.C. 1438(c)) is repealed.</div>
            <div class="ex5">(b) Repeal of Section 21A.--Section 21A of the Federal Home Loan Bank Act (12 U.S.C. 1441a) is repealed.</div>
         </div>
