                        </div>
                        <div class="ex8">(iv) in subclause (IV) (as so redesignated), by striking ``or'';</div>
                     </div>
                     <div class="ex7">(B) in clause (ii), by striking the period at the end and inserting a semicolon; and</div>
                     <div class="ex7">
                        (C) by adding at the end the following: 
