                        <div class="ex8">``(i) is violating or has violated any provision of this title, or any rule or regulation issued under this title; or</div>
                        <div class="ex8">``(ii) is or was a cause of the violation of any provision of this title, or any rule or regulation issued under this title.''.</div>
                     </div>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ex5" Notes_1="Courts.">
               (b) Extraterritorial Jurisdiction of the Antifraud Provisions of the Federal Securities Laws.--
               <div class="ex6">
