                     <div class="ex8">(i) by striking ``municipal securities brokers and municipal securities dealers'' and inserting ``municipal securities brokers, municipal securities dealers, and municipal advisors''; and</div>
                     <div class="ex8">(ii) by striking ``municipal securities broker or municipal securities dealer'' and inserting ``municipal securities broker, municipal securities dealer, or municipal advisor'';</div>
                  </div>
