                     <div class="ex7">
                        ``(A) a major market disturbance characterized by or constituting--
                        <div class="ex8">``(i) sudden and excessive fluctuations of securities prices generally, or a substantial threat thereof, that threaten fair and orderly markets; or</div>
                        <div class="ex8">``(ii) a substantial disruption of the safe or efficient operation of the national system for clearance and settlement of transactions in securities, or a substantial threat thereof; or</div>
                     </div>
