                        <div class="ex8">``(ii) Use of model not required.--No provision of this paragraph may be construed to require a financial institution to use any such model form prescribed by the Bureau.</div>
                        <div class="ex8">``(iii) Compliance using model.--A financial institution shall be deemed to be in compliance with subparagraph (A) if the financial institution uses any model form prescribed by the Bureau under this subparagraph, or the financial institution uses any such model form and rearranges its format.'';</div>
                     </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="ex7">(B) in subsection (a)(8), by inserting ``, in consultation with the Federal Trade Commission, the Federal banking agencies, and the National Credit Union Administration,'' before ``shall jointly''; and</div>
